lemma posaux4[rule_format]: "singleCombinators [a] \<longrightarrow> a\<noteq> DenyAll \<longrightarrow> b \<noteq> DenyAll \<longrightarrow> in_list a l \<longrightarrow>in_list b l \<longrightarrow> smaller a b l\<longrightarrow> x = (bothNet a) \<longrightarrow> y = (bothNet b) \<longrightarrow> position x l <= position y l"
